                        <note n="1" xml:id="note-t-1">
                            

<p>On his way from Paris to the South, <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#_1350">Signac</rs> had visited Van Gogh on 23 and 24 March (<ref target="let752.xml">see letter 752</ref>). Cassis is south-east of Marseille, on the Mediterranean Sea.</p>
                        </note>
                        
                    
                        <note n="2" xml:id="note-t-2">
                            

<p>For <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#_1350">Signac</rs>’s letter to Theo, <ref target="let752.xml#n-1">see letter 752, n. 1.</ref></p>
